{"tid":1697623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉模式] 今個星期日搞十八區打工仔集氣大會 搵工會落區收會員","createTime":"2019-11-07T03:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T04:36:06.000Z","uid":84408,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fc4e0f5131bc7b69ab6dd03b525cb0744e96cd21","tid":1697623,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:22:42.000Z","msg":"講明先 我係支持保持抗爭情緒<br />\n呢樣嘢好重要<br />\n<br />\n但我見到好似每個星期都有人想 keep 住一星期一遊行<br />\n<br />\n可惜嘅係每次都係星期四 星期五左右先吹雞 變相人少 又再大逃亡<br />\n<br />\n突發呢樣嘢真係用得太多 導致到我身邊有啲手足都開始選擇性咁去 長遠黎講是聚唔到人的<br />\n<br />\n反而出邊呢加罷工風吹得咁勁<br />\n更應該搞十八區打工仔集氣大會<br />\n<br />\n搵工會落區收會員 趁機會集中搞大勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次對象係和理非 個模式要盡量和平<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解6 7月嘅時候仲識和勇 梅花間竹<br />\n到8 9月就開始非勇不可 一和就屌人老母<br />\n<br />\n要留意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地要贏一定和勇合一 好似71當日咁"},{"pid":"ef3f38135c4b283decdb00ddebf8dfa774b99aea","tid":1697623,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:24:54.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無哂和理非活動"},{"pid":"f28668cba33baa9d3dd79f90f8a483f24b176211","tid":1697623,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:26:43.000Z","msg":"自推十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b957380633fc125ff6d6d54b647b24453e5e533","tid":1697623,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:29:09.000Z","msg":"自推 十連第二<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e085405b4c93960fc208056aecad429a4a40233","tid":1697623,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:33:25.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c97c403e0ac2007a2c74cd61429baa75da693ae","tid":1697623,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:37:29.000Z","msg":"自